room_title: Escape room "Breakout" by Escape Room BCS in College Station
room_address: 907 Harvey Rd Ste B College Station, TX 77840
room_description: Your partner has been wrongly accused of a crime and arrested by the corrupt local sheriff. Sheriff Brutus McLarren is notorious for shakedowns and your friend is in his jail. Brutus only leaves him unattended for one hour while he's away on a break. If Brutus returns and you're still in his office you'll be reunited with your friend for a very long time (after you recover at the infirmary)!
